Package: shinyTZ
Type: Package
Title: Timezone-Aware Date and Time Rendering for Shiny
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2026-01-21
Authors@R: person("Gregory", "Warnes", 
                  email = "warnes@binghamton.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides drop-in replacements for Shiny's text outputs that 
    automatically handle timezone conversion based on the user's browser 
    timezone. Eliminates the common problem of server timestamps being 
    displayed in the wrong timezone for remote users.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    shiny (>= 1.7.0),
    lubridate (>= 1.9.0),
    htmltools
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    DBI,
    dplyr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/gwarnes-mdsol/shinyTZ
BugReports: https://github.com/gwarnes-mdsol/shinyTZ/issues
